    public interface PropertyRestrictionAxiom
extends RestrictionAxiom
    A representation of the model object 'Property Restriction Axiom'. PropertyRestrictionAxiom is an axiom that places some restriction on the value of a property in the context of the restricting classifier domain. It can be specified directly on the classifier or indirectly on a reference to it.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owning Classifier
    • Owning Reference
